org.sxb.http.converter.json

クラス FastJsonHttpMessageConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sxb.http.converter.AbstractHttpMessageConverter<java.lang.Object>
      • org.sxb.http.converter.json.FastJsonHttpMessageConverter
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    HttpMessageConverter<java.lang.Object>

    public class FastJsonHttpMessageConverter
extends AbstractHttpMessageConverter<java.lang.Object>
    Implementation of HttpMessageConverter that can read and write JSON using fastJson1.26

    This converter can be used to bind to typed beans, or untyped HashMap instances.

    By default, this converter supports application/json and application/*+json. This can be overridden by setting the supportedMediaTypes property.

    Compatible with fastJson 1.2.6 and higher.

    導入されたバージョン:
    2.0
    作成者:
    Jeffson
